Subject: [PATCH] feat(starry): add ptrace(2) subset for self-hosting

Implement TRACEME/ATTACH/DETACH/CONT/SYSCALL/SINGLESTEP/KILL,
PEEK/POKE data, GET/SETREGS, and GETSIGINFO with per-process
ptrace state, waitpid WUNTRACED reporting, and tracee hooks
around syscalls, execve post-exec SIGTRAP, and x86 debug traps.

Made-with: Cursor

